I bought this for my sons birthday. All I can say is WOW.  Great still shots.  And I was blown away by the video.  The video was 100% better then some of the SD video camera! This camera is a keeper. I bought a 
class 6 - 8 GB card. I can have 60 min of video or around 1900 pictures. :)
This is my next camera.
